com.gl.vn.me.ko.sample.instrumentation.env.misc

Class CommandLineHelper.CommandLineParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gl.vn.me.ko.sample.instrumentation.env.misc.CommandLineHelper.CommandLineParams
  • Enclosing class:
    CommandLineHelper

    public static final class CommandLineHelper.CommandLineParams
extends Object
    This class defines possible application command-line arguments as described in JCommander documentation. It also contains classes for converting string representation of command line arguments to appropriate Java-objects.

    Instantiability: allowed only from inside CommandLineHelper class.
    Mutability: mutable.
    Thread safety: not thread-safe.

      This class provides a method to convert a value command line-argument into Java-object with the same type as logLevel field.
